under project folder:

for frontend:
npx create-react-app frontend - npx runs the latest version directly from npm
npm start -to start frontend
npm install firebase
npm install react-router-dom
npm install react-icons

for backend:
npm init -y
npm install express cors
node server.js - to start backend server

to make sure backend files refresh automatically when changes happen:
npm install -g nodemon
npm install nodemon --save-dev
nodemon server.js - to start backend server

